1
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,000
Boss Nan

2
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,920
Lang Jiu is useless.

3
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,599
So, for the upcoming match...

4
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,120
leave it to me.

5
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,359
How can that be?

6
00:01:38,439 --> 00:01:39,319
There's no red mole.

7
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,840
Since you want to see it so badly...

8
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,040
take a good look once and for all.

9
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:49,640
I didn't expect...

10
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,680
you're such a sentimental fool.

11
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,120
What did Jiang Nanshuo do to you?

12
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:00,719
Our relationship...

13
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:02,319
isn't close enough to discuss intimate matters.

14
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,000
I suggest you get lost right now.

15
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,319
Boss Nan.

16
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,680
Why are you so forward today?

17
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:26,840
What?

18
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,199
Don't you like it?

19
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,360
Only you can make me feel at ease.

20
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,039
Boss Nan.

21
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,319
Don't be in such a rush.

22
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:44,599
Boss Nan.

23
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:46,840
How about...

24
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,479
we play a little game?

25
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,400
I hide...

26
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,599
and you seek.

27
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,280
If you catch me...

28
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,479
then we can...

29
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,439
All right.

30
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:56,840
Let's start now.

31
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,039
Ten.

32
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,919
Nine.

33
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,879
Eight.

34
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:12,919
Let go of me!

35
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:14,199
Let me go!

36
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:19,319
Put me down!

37
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,639
Put me down!

38
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,879
Are you playing the hero saving the damsel?

39
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:28,159
Do you realize the danger you're in?

40
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:29,199
I told you, I'm not Long Weiwei.

41
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:30,400
How many times do I have to say it?

42
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,560
The Long Weiwei from ten years ago...

43
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,000
died in that fire long ago.

44
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,560
I advise you to stop pestering me.

45
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,360
That fire consumed not only Long Weiwei...

46
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,199
but me as well.

47
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,960
Are you really not her?

48
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,080
Three.

49
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,240
Two.

50
00:04:14,639 --> 00:04:15,159
One.

51
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:19,120
I'm coming, sweetheart.

52
00:04:43,959 --> 00:04:45,519
Heads or tails?

53
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:46,759
Tails.

54
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,000
I guess heads.

55
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,680
It seems...

56
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:01,120
your luck is even worse than your skills.

57
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,000
Nice shot.

58
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,800
Good!

59
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,399
Good, good, good!

60
00:06:14,399 --> 00:06:14,879
Brilliant!

61
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,160
That was truly brilliant!

62
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,720
I bet my entire fortune...

63
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,079
just to get on this yacht.

64
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,600
Seems it wasn't a waste of time.

65
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:22,600
Come on.

66
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:24,000
You want to beat me?

67
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,160
It won't be that easy.

68
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,480
Double hit foul. Change of possession.

69
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,879
Was that a double hit?

70
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:35,879
It was too far to see clearly.

71
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,959
You got lucky and won last time.

72
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,240
This time...

73
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,240
it's my turn.

74
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:04,360
This...

75
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:07,959
Quick!

76
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,879
I want him to lose everything.

77
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:18,600
Boss Nan.

78
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,759
I have a plan.

79
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,800
If I make him lose...

80
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,439
give the Nine Heavens Media business

81
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,079
to me.

82
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:42,959
Deal.

83
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:45,160
Then use that face of yours...

84
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:47,839
to really get to him.

85
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,399
Don't worry.

86
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,879
I'll make sure he loses...

87
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:56,560
willingly.

88
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,199
In a moment...

89
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,279
hit the 8-ball right at my face.

90
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:10,319
But then...

91
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,600
wouldn't that be a foul?

92
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:12,839
If you want to win...

93
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,759
do exactly as I say.

94
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,759
Hei Ba.

95
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,920
You're going to lose this time.

96
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,279
Yi Xin.

97
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:46,480
You asked for this.

98
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:32,000
Weiwei.

99
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,360
This is the championship gift

100
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:39,000
Weiwei meant for you.

101
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,200
He's gonna win.

102
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,159
We made a killing.

103
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:20,799
Yeah.

104
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:21,519
Free ball.

105
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,240
It's a sure win.

106
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:25,039
Hei Ba! Hei Ba!

107
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,639
Hei Ba! Hei Ba! Hei Ba!

108
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:30,559
Hei Ba! Hei Ba! Hei Ba!

109
00:10:30,799 --> 00:10:33,399
Hei Ba! Hei Ba! Hei Ba!

110
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:36,000
What's wrong?

111
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,000
Seeing that face...

112
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,679
are your legs getting weak?

113
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,879
Or is it that...

114
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:47,759
you remembered back in the fire,

115
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,559
just how powerless you were?

116
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:26,919
Ten whole years.

117
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:29,159
You've finally fallen at my feet.

118
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:40,120
Weren't you high and mighty?

119
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,759
Weren't you so arrogant?

120
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,799
What genius?

121
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,279
What Triple Crown Champion?

122
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,840
It's all trash.

123
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,360
Starting today,

124
00:11:57,759 --> 00:11:59,639
there is only one king in billiards.

125
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,399
And that is me,

126
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,399
Lang Jiu.

127
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:34,879
Let me go!

128
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:35,799
Let me go!

129
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:37,000
Let me out!

130
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,639
Let me go!
